 23 in a single day, reaches 40|last=Joshi|first=Manas|date=2020-04-05|website=www.indiatvnews.com|language=en|access-date=2020-04-07}}</ref>\n|-\n|[[Maharashtra]]\n|23\n|2\n|<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.saharasamay.com/nation-news/676621404/maharashtra-sees-60-new-coronavirus-cases-total-1-078.html|title=Maharashtra sees 60 new coronavirus cases, total 1,078|website=Sahara Samay|access-date=2020-04-08}}</ref>\n|-\n|[[Odisha]]\n|{{ndash}}\n|{{ndash}}\n|\n|-\n|[[Puducherry]]\n|2\n|{{ndash}}\n|<ref name=\":12\" />\n|-\n|[[2020 coronavirus pandemic in Punjab, India|Punjab]]\n|26\n|{{ndash}}\n|<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.jagran.com/punjab/chandigarh-corona-virus-attack-intensified-in-punjab-and-20-positive-cases-confirmed-in-a-single-day-20173900.html|title=\u092a\u0902\u091c\u093e\u092c \u092e\u0947\u0902 \u0924\u0947\u091c \u0939\u0941\u0906 \u0915\u094b\u0930\u094b\u0928\u093e \u0935\u093e\u092f\u0930\u0938 \u0915\u093e \u0939\u092e\u0932\u093e, \u090f\u0915 \u0939\u0940 \u0926\u093f\u0928 \u092e\u0947\u0902 20 \u092a\u0949\u091c\u093f\u091f\u093f\u0935 \u0915\u0947\u0938 \u0915\u0940 \u092a\u0941\u0937\u094d\u091f\u093f, \u091b\u0939 \u091c\u092e\u093e\u0924\u0940|website=Dainik Jagran|language=hi|access-date=2020-04-08}}</ref>\n|-\n|[[Rajasthan]]\n|43\n|{{ndash}}\n|<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.freepressjournal.in/india/coronavirus-in-rajasthan-tablighi-jamaat-members-tested-positive-across-various-districts-positive-cases-of-covid-19-touches-200|title=Coronavirus in Rajasthan: Tablighi Jamaat members tested positive across various districts; positive cases of COVID-19 touches 200|website=Free Press Journal|language=en|access-date=2020-04-07}}</ref>\n|-\n|[[2020 coronavirus pandemic in Tamil Nadu|Tamil Nadu]]\n|1113\n|2\n|<ref>{{cite web|url=https://twitter.com/ANI/status/1250419244992323584/photo/2|title=38 more #COVID19 cases reported in Tamil Nadu today, of these 34 are those who attended \"single source event in Delhi\" & their contacts. Total coronavir